      • registerDefaults

        public MediaSupport.Builder registerDefaults()
        Register the default readers and writers.

        Default readers

        • StringBodyReader - converts payload into String.class
        • InputStreamBodyReader - converts payload into InputStream.class

        Default writers

        • CharSequenceBodyWriter - generates payload from CharSequence.class
        • ByteChannelBodyWriter - generates payload from ReadableByteChannel.class
        • PathBodyWriter - generates payload from Path.class
        • FileBodyWriter - generates payload from File.class
        • ThrowableBodyWriter - generates payload from Throwable.class
        Returns:
        this MediaSupport.Builder
